%% Diagram: Search ingestion pipeline — CDC from Postgres to OpenSearch with alias swap
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    PG[(Postgres\nissues, comments)]
    OUTBOX["Outbox table\n(transactional)"]
    DEBEZ["CDC\n(Debezium / logical replication)"]
    KAFKA["Kafka\nissue.changes"]
    INDEXER["Indexer worker\n(denormalize + project to doc)"]
    OS_LIVE[("OpenSearch\nissues_v42 (alias: issues)")]
    OS_NEW[("OpenSearch\nissues_v43 (rebuild)")]
    QUERY["Search API\n(BM25 + filters + facets)"]

    PG --> OUTBOX --> DEBEZ --> KAFKA --> INDEXER
    INDEXER -->|incremental| OS_LIVE
    INDEXER -.->|reindex job| OS_NEW
    OS_NEW -.->|atomic alias swap| OS_LIVE
    QUERY --> OS_LIVE
